OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,FAfter sentencing, Gosport MP Caroline
OL,8,FDinenage wrote to Ellie Reeves
OL,9,Fexpressing the feelings of the
OL,10,Ffamilies involved that the sentence
OL,11,Fwas not severe enough.
OL,13,FThe solicitor general has confirmed
OL,14,Fthat the case will go to the Court of
OL,15,FAppeal under the Unduly Lenient
OL,16,FSentence (ULS) scheme.
OL,18,FIn a letter to the Conservative MP, Ms
OL,19,FReeves wrote: "I share your concerns
OL,20,Fabout the sentence imposed, which I
OL,21,Fhave now reviewed.
OL,26,@{D@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,F"Under the ULS scheme, I can only
OL,8,Fproperly refer a case to the Court of
OL,9,FAppeal if I consider that the sentence
OL,10,Fappears not just lenient, but unduly
OL,11,Flenient.
OL,13,F"After careful consideration I have
OL,14,Fdecided to refer this case to the
OL,15,FCourt of Appeal as it appears to me
OL,16,Fthat this test is met."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
