PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,FPosting on Facebook, Ms Dinenage said:
OL,8,F"The families impacted by this case
OL,9,Fbelieve that the original sentence was
OL,10,Funduly lenient and I look forward to
OL,11,Fthe outcome of the case."
OL,13,FStatements from 13 family members of
OL,14,Floved ones who were in the care of
OL,15,FElkin and Bell were read to the court,
OL,16,Fwith some saying the uncertainty of
OL,17,Fhow they were treated in death would
OL,18,Fhaunt them forever.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
