PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,FThe court heard details of some loved
OL,8,Fones covered in maggots, shedding skin
OL,9,Fand lying in their own fluids as they
OL,10,Fwere decomposing, kept in
OL,11,Funrefrigerated conditions.
OL,13,FDuring the trial, the court heard the
OL,14,Fbodies of two elderly men were found
OL,15,Fby High Court enforcement agents who
OL,16,Fhad been tasked with repossessing the
OL,17,Fpremises because of unpaid rent and
OL,18,Fdebts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,FThe case, along with the case of Hull
OL,8,Ffuneral director Robert Bush, has
OL,9,Fprompted calls for urgent regulation
OL,10,Fof the funeral sector, including from
OL,11,Fbereaved families, police bosses and
OL,12,Fan industry body.
OL,14,FPolice found 35 bodies and more than
OL,15,F100 sets of ashes when they raided
OL,16,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors'
OL,17,Fin Hull in March 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
