PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777611881
OL,3,CFuneral directors' 'unduly lenient'
OL,4,Cprison sentence referred to Court of
OL,5,CAppeal
OL,7,FBush pleaded guilty at Hull Crown
OL,8,FCourt to 30 counts of preventing a
OL,9,Flawful and decent burial over 30 of
OL,10,Fthe bodies ` one of which had been
OL,11,Fthere for a year.
OL,13,FThe 48-year-old, who also pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to theft from 12 charities
OL,15,Fincluding the Salvation Army and
OL,16,FMacmillan Cancer Support, will be
OL,17,Fsentenced in July.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
